<doc>
  <member name="D3D12_TEX2D_UAV">
    <summary>
      <para>Describes a unordered-access 2D texture resource.</para>
    </summary>
    <remarks>
      <para>Use this structure with a <see cref="D3D12_UNORDERED_ACCESS_VIEW_DESC" /> structure to view the resource as a 2D texture.</para>
    </remarks>
    <seealso href="https://docs.microsoft.com//windows/desktop/direct3d12/direct3d-12-structures">Core Structures</seealso>
  </member>
  <member name="D3D12_TEX2D_UAV.MipSlice">
    <summary>
      <para>The mipmap slice index.</para>
    </summary>
  </member>
  <member name="D3D12_TEX2D_UAV.PlaneSlice">
    <summary>
      <para>The index (plane slice number) of the plane to use in the texture.</para>
    </summary>
  </member>
</doc>